org.jscsi.target.connection
Class TargetSession

java.lang.Object
  org.jscsi.target.connection.TargetSession

public class TargetSession
extends java.lang.Object

A class for objects representing an iSCSI session with all necessary variables.

Currently, a TargetSession can only have one TargetConnection, i.e. MaxConnections=1.

Author:
Andreas Ergenzinger
